snippet.title: School of Devops
snippet.description: School of Devops is a specialised training school which offers the most comprehensive, career oriented training programs in the field of devops.  Capabilities include Cloud Computing, Infrastructure as a Code,  Configuration Management, Continuous Integration and Delivery,  Containers and Micro Services.  Tools covered are Chef, Puppet, Docker, Ansible, Kubernetes, Jenkins, Git, AWS, Sonarqube, Artifactory   and more.
